            <!-- About Me Section -->
            <div id="about-me-card" class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-all hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                <!-- English Paragraph -->
                <p id="about-text-en" class="text-left text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-4"> 
                    I am a web developer. I like to play sports. I like to watch the Ravens and Cavs. I like pancakes and syrup. I'm South Asian. I like my computer.
